channel.title: Run error
channel.description:
Well ive seen a lot of others with this problem but no real response. Ive had my source for awhile now and I do know basic java- so you dont have to go ALL noob on me :D. Just today when I try to log on my main admin account- and a new account same error occurs.
[code] Jb Blaze signing into server
chacracterfile not found: Moreinfo file not found:
[/code]
in an attempt to log in again i now get this along with it
[code] Jb Blaze is already logged in[/code]
Im not even sure were to BEGIN looking for this type of error. Im sure this is gonna be a pain in the neck. But if any has any past experience on this id appreciate a response.
Thanks.
